General.Name: CodeMill AB
General.Description: CodeMill AB (publ), a tech company, provides media workflow applications in Sweden and internationally. It offers Accurate.Video, a web-based platform for video production created for media companies and other companies; Accurate Player SDK, a web browser based professional video, audio, and subtitle player framework; and Cantemo, a media management platform that helps customers get order and structure in their media library. The company serves video and media companies. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Umeå, Sweden.
